'''任-{}-德龙'''<ref name="#1">{{cite web|title=華裔好友代取中文名「賀錦麗」：祝賀…前程似錦|url=https://www.worldjournal.com/7093304/|accessdate=2020-10-10|author=|date=2020-08-12|format=|publisher=|language=zh-hant|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010044127/https://www.worldjournal.com/7093304/|archivedate=2020-10-10|website=世界日報|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原名音译为'''道格拉斯·克雷格·埃姆霍夫'''（{{lang-en|Douglas Craig Emhoff}}；{{bd|1964年|10月13日||}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.cankaoxiaoxi.com/culture/culture20210209/2434521.shtml?fr=mb |title=参考消息：道格·埃姆霍夫：美国首位“第二先生” |access-date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2022-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416162218/http://m.cankaoxiaoxi.com/culture/culture20210209/2434521.shtml?fr=mb }}</ref><ref>[http://m.cankaoxiaoxi.com/world/20201115/2424784.shtml?fr=mb 参考消息：美媒：美国准“第二先生”埃姆霍夫将甘当绿叶 以哈里斯事业为重]</ref><ref>[https://m.gmw.cn/2020-12/11/content_1301929500.htm 光明网：美国首位“第二先生”将开启新职业：在华盛顿任教]</ref>，是一名[[美国|美国]]律师，第49任[[美国副总统|美国副总统]][[賀錦麗|賀錦麗]]的丈夫，也是美国历史上首位[[美國副總統配偶|第二先生]]。

== 姓名 ==
其本人中文名是妻子[[賀錦麗|賀錦麗]]的好友、加州保險局律師顧問蘇榮麗和她的僑領父親蘇錫芬給取的，當他得知蘇榮麗為妻子取過一個中文名字後，也請求蘇榮麗為自己取名，還希望名字裡有個「龍」字，於是蘇榮麗給他取了「任-{}-德龍」這個名字<ref name="#1"/>。

==早年与教育==
任德龙于[[纽约|纽约]][[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]一個猶太裔家庭出生，1969年至1981年住在[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]，青少年期间随家人迁居加利福尼亚州<ref name="app-nj">{{cite news |last1=Davis |first1=Mike |title=Kamala Harris' husband, Douglas Emhoff, has 'NJ in his veins' |url=https://www.app.com/story/news/politics/2020/08/12/kamala-harris-joe-biden-douglas-emhoff-vice-president/3356770001/ |accessdate=2020-08-12 |newspaper={{tsl|en|Asbury Park Press||Asbury Park Press}} |date=2020-08-12}}</ref><ref name="cnn-what-to-know">{{cite news |last1=Reston |first1=Maeve |title=What to know about Douglas Emhoff, Kamala Harris' husband, after that onstage protester moment |url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/06/02/politics/who-is-douglas-emhoff-kamala-harris-husband/index.html |accessdate=2020-08-11 |website=CNN |date=2019-06-03 |archive-date=2019-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709194650/https://www.cnn.com/2019/06/02/politics/who-is-douglas-emhoff-kamala-harris-husband/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|first=Gabe|last=Friedman|date=2020-08-11|title=Kamala Harris is Joe Biden's VP pick - here's what Jewish voters should know|url=https://www.jta.org/2020/08/11/politics/kamala-harris-is-joe-bidens-vp-pick-heres-what-jewish-voters-should-know|access-date=2020-08-12|agency={{tsl|en|Jewish Telegraphic Agency||Jewish Telegraphic Agency}}|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812161608/https://www.jta.org/2020/08/11/politics/kamala-harris-is-joe-bidens-vp-pick-heres-what-jewish-voters-should-know|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他毕业于{{tsl|en|Agoura High School|阿古拉高中}}，获[[加州州立大學北嶺分校|加州州立大學北嶺分校]]文学士、[[南加州大学古尔德法学院|南加州大学古尔德法学院]][[法律博士|法律博士]]学位<ref name="thr-first">{{cite magazine |last1=Cullins |first1=Ashley |title=First Gentleman? Kamala Harris' Attorney Husband Talks 'Endlessly Fascinating' Campaign Trail |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kamala-harris-attorney-husband-talks-fascinating-campaign-trail-1197098 |magazine=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2019-03-29 |accessdate=2020-08-11 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330160209/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kamala-harris-attorney-husband-talks-fascinating-campaign-trail-1197098 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==生涯==
任德龙是娱乐行业诉讼律师，首份工作任职于{{le|必百瑞|Pillsbury Winthrop Shaw Pittman}}律师事务所诉讼小组。随后于1990年代转到精品服饰品牌Belin Rawlings & Badal工作。2000年，他与本·惠特威尔（Ben Whitwell）合伙开设事务所，客户包括[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]和[[默克藥廠|默克藥廠]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Saul|first=Stephanie|date=2020-08-17|title=Doug Emhoff, Kamala Harris’s husband, takes a leave of absence from his law firm.|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/17/us/elections/doug-emhoff-kamala-harriss-husband-takes-a-leave-of-absence-from-his-law-firm.html|access-date=2020-08-19|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819001927/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/17/us/elections/doug-emhoff-kamala-harriss-husband-takes-a-leave-of-absence-from-his-law-firm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年被{{tsl|en|Venable LLP|Venable LLP|Venable}}收购，随后成为Venable[[美国西岸|美国西岸]]办公室常务董事<ref>{{Cite web|last=Greene|first=Jenna|date=2020-08-13|title=Westlaw Today Signon|url=https://today.westlaw.com/Document/I59b44f00dda611ea9e9b9b34449fe282/View/FullText.html?transitionType=Default&contextData=(sc.Default)&VR=3.0&RS=cblt1.0|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010044128/https://today.westlaw.com/Document/I59b44f00dda611ea9e9b9b34449fe282/View/FullText.html?transitionType=Default&contextData=(sc.Default)&VR=3.0&RS=cblt1.0&firstPage=true|archive-date=2020-10-10|access-date=2020-08-19|website=signon.thomsonreuters.com}}</ref>。

2017年，任德龙以合伙人身份加入{{tsl|en|DLA Piper|DLA Piper}}律师事务所，任职于[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]和加州的办公室<ref name="ap-growing">{{cite news|last1=Summers|first1=Juana|date=2019-06-08|title=Harris’ husband takes on growing public role in 2020 race|agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|url=https://apnews.com/1b5e33b807fe48fb9d7e7bcc79547af7|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820090852/https://apnews.com/1b5e33b807fe48fb9d7e7bcc79547af7|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Bonos|first=Lisa|last2=|date=2020-08-19|title=The story of Kamala and Doug, a match made in Hollywood (literally)|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/relationships/doug-emhoff-kamala-harris-husband/2020/08/18/a6c64db6-e15c-11ea-8181-606e603bb1c4_story.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819180557/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/relationships/doug-emhoff-kamala-harris-husband/2020/08/18/a6c64db6-e15c-11ea-8181-606e603bb1c4_story.html|archive-date=2020-08-19|access-date=2020-08-19|website=Washington Post|language=en}}</ref>。贺锦丽宣布成为乔·拜登在[[2020美国总统选举|2020美国总统选举]]中的竞选搭档后，任德龙向DLA Piper请假<ref name=":1" />。

==个人生活==
任德龙与第一任妻子{{tsl|en|Kerstin Emhoff|克斯汀·埃姆霍夫|克斯汀·麦金}}结婚16年，育有两子科尔（Cole）和艾拉（Ella）<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Harris|first=Kamala|date=2019-05-10|title=Sen. Kamala Harris on Being 'Momala'|url=https://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/a27422434/kamala-harris-stepmom-mothers-day/|access-date=2020-08-12|magazine=Elle|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812185005/https://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/a27422434/kamala-harris-stepmom-mothers-day/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0" />。2014年8月22日，在贺锦丽妹妹{{tsl|en|Maya Harris|玛雅·哈里斯}}的主持下，[[贺锦丽|贺锦丽]]与任德龙结婚<ref>{{cite news|last=Siders|first=David|date=2014-08-25|title=Kamala Harris married in Santa Barbara ceremony|work={{tsl|en|The Sacramento Bee||The Sacramento Bee}}|url=https://www.sacbee.com/news/politics-government/capitol-alert/article2607685.html|accessdate=2020-10-10|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817181737/https://www.sacbee.com/news/politics-government/capitol-alert/article2607685.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2019年8月，夫妇俩的资产净值约为580万美元<ref name="forbes">{{cite news|date=2019-08-14|title=The Net Worth Of Every 2020 Presidential Candidate|work=Forbes|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/danalexander/2019/08/14/heres-the-net-worth-of-every-2020-presidential-candidate/|accessdate=2019-08-24|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823194359/https://www.forbes.com/sites/danalexander/2019/08/14/heres-the-net-worth-of-every-2020-presidential-candidate/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

贺锦丽曾参加[[2020年美國總統選舉民主黨初選|2020年美國總統選舉民主黨初選]]，但于2019年12月被淘汰，此前任德龙曾多次陪同贺锦丽出席竞选活动<ref name="cnn-what-to-know"/>。2020年8月11日，贺锦丽獲[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]選為在[[2020年美国总统大选|2020年美国总统大选]]的竞选搭档，使得任德龙成为继{{tsl|en|John Zaccaro|约翰·扎卡罗}}和{{tsl|en|Todd Palin|托德·佩林}}后，主要政党副总统候选人中的第三位男性配偶<ref>{{cite news|last=Emmrich|first=Stuart|date=2020-08-13|title=The 9 Things We Know About Kamala Harris’s Husband|work=[[时尚_(Vogue)|Vogue]]|url=https://www.vogue.com/article/nine-things-we-know-about-kamala-harris-husband-douglas-emhoff|accessdate=2020-08-15|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906171652/https://www.vogue.com/article/nine-things-we-know-about-kamala-harris-husband-douglas-emhoff|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後贺锦丽成功当选，任德龙成為美国首位[[美国第二夫人|第二先生]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Edelman|first=Adam|date=2020-08-13|title=The first 'second gentleman'? Meet Kamala Harris' husband, Doug Emhoff|work=[[NBC新聞|NBC News]]|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2020-election/first-second-gentleman-meet-kamala-harris-husband-doug-emhoff-n1236554|accessdate=2020-08-15|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815021438/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2020-election/first-second-gentleman-meet-kamala-harris-husband-doug-emhoff-n1236554|dead-url=no}}</ref>、首位犹太裔[[美国副总统|副总统]]配偶<ref name="vc-star">{{cite news |last1=Kisken |first1=Tom |title=Agoura High alumnus could become nation's first 'second gentleman' |url=https://www.vcstar.com/story/news/local/2020/08/26/who-is-kamala-harris-husband-doug-emhoff-married-agoura-high-school/3415297001/ |accessdate=2020-08-27 |publisher=Ventura County Star |date=2020-08-26 |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010044126/https://www.vcstar.com/story/news/local/2020/08/26/who-is-kamala-harris-husband-doug-emhoff-married-agoura-high-school/3415297001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-13|title=Douglas Emhoff: Kamala Harris's husband and potential 'second gentleman'|language=en-gb|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53758915|access-date=2020-08-17|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816221840/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53758915|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Schor|first=Elana|date=2020-08-12|title=Harris brings Baptist, interfaith roots to Democratic ticket|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/religion/harris-brings-baptist-interfaith-roots-to-democratic-ticket/2020/08/12/2d319e6a-dc57-11ea-b4f1-25b762cdbbf4_story.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903200811/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/religion/harris-brings-baptist-interfaith-roots-to-democratic-ticket/2020/08/12/2d319e6a-dc57-11ea-b4f1-25b762cdbbf4_story.html|archive-date=2020-09-03|access-date=2020-08-17|newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]]|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":1" />。

